Pingeolo,is,a,geolocation,provider,with,local,data,features,such,as,longitude,latitude,weather,and,timezone,It,also,offers,an,IP,geolocation,database,for,countries,which,supports,applications,with,localized,search,results,priced,plans,are,available,and,a,free,trial,is,available,as,well,Developers,need,to,register,to,access,API,documentation,The,Pingeolo,uses,API,Keys,for,authentication,and,responds,in,JSON,format,requests,are,made,through,HTTP